item.title: Episode #201 ... Resistance, Love, and the importance of Failure. (Zizek, Byung Chul Han)
item.description: Today we talk about a potential way to find meaning for someone prone to postmodern subjectivity. We talk about surplus enjoyment. Zizek's alcohol use, or lack thereof.
